NOTE ON BINARY ARTIFACTS

This license applies to the code authored by the project (notably the
`macho2elf/` directory). Files under `vendor/` are unmodified Apple Mach-O
dylibs extracted from Apple's tvOS Simulator Runtime; their distribution here
is for technical demonstration of the conversion process. They remain subject
to Apple's SDK and software license terms. Files under `prebuilt/` are derived
from those Apple binaries via this project's conversion script and inherit
that same legal posture.

If you intend to redistribute or productize this work, build the converted
binaries from your own copy of the simulator runtime (see docs/01-extraction.md).

