THIRD-PARTY NOTICES

This project incorporates code, declarations, or build artifacts derived from
the following third-party sources. Each notice below is reproduced as required
by the upstream license.

1) ECI 6.x C API constants and enum declarations
   -------------------------------------------------------------------------
   The enum values and struct declarations in `sd_eloquence/src/eci/eci.h`
   are an independent reimplementation of the public ABI declarations from
   IBM's ECI 6.x SDK (specifically `eci.h` from pyibmtts-sdk, also reproduced
   verbatim at `docs/ibm-sdk/eci.h`). The signatures are byte-for-byte
   identical to IBM's so the same compiled engine binaries link cleanly, but
   the declarations themselves are not copied verbatim.

   Out of respect for IBM's attribution requirements on the original
   declarations, the following copyright and BSD-3-Clause notice from
   `docs/ibm-sdk/eci.h` is reproduced here in full:

   Copyright (c) 2005, 2006, IBM Corp. All rights reserved.

